    • swen221.lab2.rules中Rule的使用

      实现Rule的swen221.lab2.rules中的类 
      限定符和类型 类和说明
      class  CellDecayOverPopulationRule
      This should implements Cell Decay version of Conway's rule for overproduction: "Any live cell with more than three live neighbours gets older, as if by over-population."
      class  CellDecayReproductionRule
      This should implements Cell Decay version of Conway's rule for happiness: "Any cell with exactly three live neighbours gets younger, as if by happiness."
      class  CellDecayUnderPopulationRule
      This should implements Cell Decay version of Conway's rule for under-production: "Any live cell with fewer than two live neighbours gets older, as if caused by under-population."
      class  ConwaysOverpopulationRule
      This should implements Conway's rule for overproduction: "Any live cell with more than three live neighbours dies, as if by over-population"
      class  ConwaysReproductionRule
      This should implement Conway's rule for reproduction: "Any dead cell with exactly three live neighbours becomes a live cell, as if by reproduction"
      class  ConwaysUnderpopulationRule
      This should implements Conway's rule for under-population: "Any live cell with fewer than two live neighbours dies, as if caused by under-population."
